In the INTEREST OF T.C., T.B., B.B., K.B., and C.B., Minor Children, C.B., Mother of T.C., T.B., B.B., and K.B., Appellant, J.B., Father of T.B., B.B., K.B., and C.B., Appellant. No. 19-0128 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed April 17, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and father separately appeal the termination of their parental rights to several children. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
